# Cursor 3 vs Claude Code — April 2026

## Executive Overview

**Cursor 3 sells you a product. Claude Code gives you a primitive.** That single distinction drives every other decision.

Cursor 3 (Glass, 2 April 2026) is a polished multi-agent workspace — broad model choice, mobile/web/Slack/GitHub/Linear handoff, and an Agents Window that demotes the IDE to a fallback. Best for accelerating individual engineers and small product teams *now*.

Claude Code is a thin, terminal-native, Anthropic-only agent that composes into whatever harness you operate. Best for platform teams industrialising AI inside governed, audited, ROI-instrumented environments.

**Verdict:** Run both. Cursor 3 for developer experience at the edge. Claude Code as the engine inside your enterprise AI platform.

## Metric-by-Metric Comparison

| Metric | Cursor 3 | Claude Code | Where to use what |
|---|:---:|:---:|---|
| **Out-of-box experience** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — install and go |
| **Multi-agent orchestration** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — parallel cloud/local/SSH agents |
| **Composability into platforms** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — wrap inside enterprise AI platforms |
| **Model choice (Claude/GPT/Gemini)** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — multi-model A/B testing |
| **Anthropic-standardised stack** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — when standardising on Bedrock + Claude |
| **Repo-aware autocomplete (Tab 2.0)** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — IDE-centric coding |
| **Terminal / CLI workflows** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — scripted, headless, CI |
| **MCP support** | ✅ | ✅ | Tie — both first-class |
| **Mobile, Slack, Linear, GitHub UX** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — cross-device handoff |
| **Governance, RBAC, audit fit** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — regulated enterprises |
| **Cost predictability** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — token-based, easy to forecast |
| **Background async agents** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — fire-and-forget cloud agents |
| **Worktree / parallel isolation** | ✅ | ✅ | Tie — both supported |
| **Customisation via SDK** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — Agent SDK extensibility |
| **Vendor lock-in risk** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — lower footprint |
| **Onboarding speed for engineers** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — minimal ramp-up |
| **Design / browser UI iteration** | ✅ | ❌ | Cursor 3 — Design Mode |
| **Voice STT (20 languages)** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — global teams |
| **Maturity / production stability** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — incremental, hardened releases |
| **Strategic platform foundation** | ❌ | ✅ | Claude Code — industrialised AI engineering |

**Tally:** Cursor 3 wins 9 · Claude Code wins 13 · Tie 2

**Practical pattern for a large enterprise:** Cursor 3 in the hands of senior engineers for velocity; Claude Code as the embedded engine inside your internal AI platform for governed, scaled, auditable agent workflows.

